# .cursorrules for IPCZ

- Framework: ASP.NET Core MVC (.NET 8.0)
- Database Access: ADO.NET (SqlConnection/SqlCommand) with Stored Procedures prefixed with Ipcz_
- AI Integration: Google Gemini 1.5 Flash via REST Client with fallbacks
- UI: Vanilla CSS Medical-Tech Design System, Glassmorphism, Outfit/Inter typography, 7 Theme Switcher
- Secrets: Never commit secrets to git. Always use placeholders in appsettings.json.
